          },
          "7c09213a-f301-4026-9500-307ad2df0e3e": {
            "type": "html",
            "settings": {
              "code": "<div class=\"row align-items-center layout-column-2\">\n    <div class=\"col-12 col-md-12\">\n        <div class=\"py-5 mb-4\">\n            <div class=\"py-4 pl-2\">\n                <h3 class=\"h3 bottom-title\">Looking Closely</h3>\n                <h1 class=\"text-main line-after\">What Is<br> A Biopsy?</h1>\n                <p class=\"\">The biopsy procedure if the staff at re*be decides it is necessary is done under local anesthesia or with no anesthesia. A small punch biopsy tool that looks like a tiny cookie cutter is used to remove a small amount of the abnormal skin. </p>\n<p>This skin is sent into the lap where a pathologist looks under the microscope to determine better what is wrong. Often treatment can be better planned when a more accurate diagnosis is obtained.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>",
              "width": "50%",
              "align": "auto"
            }
          },
          "f0d1861a-aaa4-48e7-8a1e-e5d6587f80ab": {
            "type": "html",
            "settings": {
              "code": "<div class=\"row align-items-center layout-column-2\">\n    <div class=\"col-12 col-md-12\">\n        <div class=\"py-5 mb-4\">\n            <div class=\"py-4 pl-2\">\n                <h3 class=\"h3 bottom-title\">Protect Your Skin</h3>\n                <h1 class=\"text-main line-after\">Stay Safe & Healthy</h1>\n                <p class=\"text-blue-main text-italic\">The biopsy usually heals without scarring or a small scar.</p>\n<p>The biopsy is not always the final perfect way to determine what to do next difficult skin lesions but can be a big help. Infection from a biopsy is uncommon and generally if the wound is kept clean it will heal with a minimum of discomfort, little or no scarring and little chance of infection.</p>\n<p>On some occasions an excision is needed to remove more of the skin or tissue if abnormalities are detected.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>",
              "width": "50%",
              "align": "auto"
            }
          },
          "7bdc1444-16a5-4add-8d71-2468d75e8079": {
            "type": "image",
            "settings": {
              "width": "50%",
