          "a4e78cd4-90ce-49de-8c71-16acb6b4c3eb": {
            "type": "html",
            "settings": {
              "code": "<div class=\"row align-items-center layout-column-2\">\n    <div class=\"col-12 col-md-12\">\n        <div class=\"py-5\">\n            <div class=\"py-4 pl-2\">\n                <h3 class=\"h3 bottom-title\">The Very Best</h3>\n                <h1 class=\"text-main line-after\">CoolSculpting® Certified Center</h1>\n                <p class=\"text-blue-main text-italic\">CoolSculpting® Certified Practice by Zeltiq.</p>\n<p>CoolSculpting® uses the advanced technology to carefully freeze your fat. Much like frostbite, freezing your fat causes it to die and your body clears it out. These changes are long term and may be permanent in some cases. The system protects your skin from freezing so the fat underneath your skin is removed.</p>\n<p>Learn more on the CoolSculpting Website</p>\n<button type=\"submit\" class=\"btn btn-theme\" name=\"commit\"><a href=\"https://www.coolsculpting.com\">\n                        <span class=\"d-none d-sm-block text-white\">Visit Website</span>\n                        <span class=\"d-block d-sm-none\"><i class=\"icon-send\"></i></span>\n                      </a></button>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>",
              "width": "50%",
              "align": "auto"
            }
          },
          "7733a837-1ad2-4007-931a-d6b057dd9f1e": {
            "type": "html",
            "settings": {
              "code": "<div class=\"row align-items-center layout-column-2\">\n    <div class=\"col-12 col-md-12\">\n        <div class=\"py-5\">\n            <div class=\"py-4 pl-2\">\n                <h3 class=\"h3 bottom-title\">The Best</h3>\n                <h3 class=\"text-main line-after\">CoolSculpting<br>\nUpper Arm</h3>\n                <p class=\"text-blue-main text-italic\">CoolSculpting® results before and after on the upper arms (Zeltiq photo).</p>\n<p>Re*be® is happy to offer coolsculpting® and excited to be able to participate in treatments that can offer results like these without downtime and without surgery. Everyone's results are different. </p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>",
              "width": "33%",
