          "60c2da8c-5a16-4394-bd2a-0881f1b249bd": {
            "type": "html",
            "settings": {
              "code": "<div class=\"row align-items-center layout-column-2\">\n    <div class=\"col-12 col-md-12\">\n        <div class=\"py-5 mb-4\">\n            <div class=\"py-4 pl-2\">\n                <h3 class=\"h3 bottom-title\">A NEW YOU</h3>\n                <h1 class=\"text-main line-after\"> Cosmetic Sclerotherapy</h1>\n                <p class=\"text-blue-main text-italic\">Cosmetic vein treatment can be done at our clinic with sclerotherapy or in some occasions with a laser.</p>\n<p>Cosmetic vein treatment is a highly effective way of eliminating unwanted spider varicose veins.  Veins can be treated cosmetically if your veins are not causing you symptoms or associated with underlying vein problems.</p>\n<p>The treatment should begin with a vein screen from our vascular technologist to confirm there is no venous disease causing the spider veins that can prevent the treatment from being successful.   The veins can be treated with sclerotherapy that is an injection procedure done in our office.  It is very similar to our medical sclerotherapy.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>",
              "width": "50%",
              "align": "auto"
            }
          }
