          "0839d7e2-8b31-49a5-acfb-79f608a8216b": {
            "type": "html",
            "settings": {
              "code": "<div class=\"row align-items-center layout-column-2\">\n    <div class=\"col-12 col-md-12\">\n        <div class=\"py-5 mb-4\">\n            <div class=\"py-4 pl-2\">\n                <h3 class=\"h3 bottom-title\">How it Works</h3>\n                <h1 class=\"text-main line-after\">Botox Injection<br>Cosmetic Basics</h1>\n                <p class=\"text-blue-main text-italic\">Botox® is used around the forehead and eyes to soften the fine lines and wrinkles.</p>\n<p>Botox® is delivered to the muscles of the face with tiny needles. It is used to relax the muscles in the skin that constantly fold the skin into fine temporary lines and later deeper lines. The body will slow or stop the process that causes these lines to form and will actually allow the skin to fill them in sometimes to a dramatic degree.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>",
              "width": "50%",
              "align": "auto"
            }
          },
          "d2321115-e983-408f-9d51-ecadfb241a38": {
            "type": "html",
            "settings": {
              "code": "<div class=\"row align-items-center layout-column-2\">\n    <div class=\"col-12 col-md-12\">\n        <div class=\"py-5 mb-4\">\n            <div class=\"py-4 pl-2\">\n                <h3 class=\"h3 bottom-title\">More Information</h3>\n                <h1 class=\"text-main line-after\">Understanding<br>Botox Injections</h1>\n                <p class=\"text-blue-main text-italic\">Botox injections for control of facial wrinkles is the most popular cosmetic procedure in the country.</p>\n<p>Botox is currently being used for many reasons, some of which are covered by insurance some are not. Botox is not permanent since your skin is constantly changing over time. Even though Botox injections don't last forever, they can last up to 4 months with some lingering effects after that. Most Botox patients come back every 6 months to get a new injection. </p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>",
              "width": "50%",
              "align": "auto"
            }
          },
          "827ee96d-7e78-4212-b2d0-3aa1081a6291": {
            "type": "html",
            "settings": {
              "code": "<iframe src=\"https://content.understand.com/kolegraffmd.player?PresentationID=9409f46c-29d9-40e5-9978-8e28acd86aa0&CatalogID=28044ef7-edc4-42e4-9bbc-b8f76ba1984c&pauseFirstStep=1\" width=\"700\" height=\"500\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" style=\"border:1px solid #f8f8f8; border-width:1px; margin-bottom:5px; max-width: 100%;\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>",
              "width": "50%",
              "align": "auto"
            }
          },
          "13d924dd-918a-4638-8225-2560358b95b3": {
            "type": "html",
            "settings": {
              "code": "<div class=\"container\">\n    <div class=\"row m-b-n30\">\n        <div class=\"col-12\">\n            <div class=\"service-long-title text-center\">\n              <h2 class=\"title\">\n                <span class=\"text-main\">Frequently Asked Questions</span> on Botox Injections.\n              </h2>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"col-12 col-lg-6 col-el-4 m-b-30\">\n            <div class=\"single-service\">\n                <div class=\"single-service-title\">\n                  <h2 class=\"title\">Do Botox injections hurt?</h2>\n                  <p>It can be briefly uncomfortable for some people and we have several ways to help control the pain if needed.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"col-12 col-lg-6 col-el-4 m-b-30\">\n            <div class=\"single-service\">\n                <div class=\"single-service-title\">\n                  <h2 class=\"title\">Are the Botox changes permanent?</h2>\n                  <p>No. The changes will usually last about 4 months but some lingering effects can be seen after that.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"col-12 col-lg-6 col-el-4 m-b-30\">\n            <div class=\"single-service\">\n                <div class=\"single-service-title\">\n                  <h2 class=\"title\">Is Botox only used for cosmetic?</h2>\n                  <p>Botox® is currently being used for many reasons such as eyelid spasms, headaches, excessive sweating and more.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"col-12 col-lg-6 col-el-4 m-b-30\">\n            <div class=\"single-service\">\n                <div class=\"single-service-title\">\n                  <h2 class=\"title\">Are there aftercare steps I should take?</h2>\n                  <p>Once treatment is completed you should avoid manipulating the area as to do so will move the Botox® into a new location.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"col-12 col-lg-6 col-el-4 m-b-30\">\n            <div class=\"single-service\">\n                <div class=\"single-service-title\">\n                  <h2 class=\"title\">Are the Botox results immediate?</h2>\n                  <p>No. It will take several days to start to see the effects of Botox after it is injected into your facial muscles.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"col-12 col-lg-6 col-el-4 m-b-30\">\n            <div class=\"single-service\">\n                <div class=\"single-service-title\">\n                  <h2 class=\"title\">How long does the Botox treatment take?</h2>\n                  <p>Depending on the number of areas treated most treatments take 5-15 minutes.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>",
              "width": "100%",
              "align": "auto"
            }
          }
        },
