          "5cfde39f-c3f5-476d-aaa5-5b3cb062c9f9": {
            "type": "html",
            "settings": {
              "code": "<div class=\"row align-items-center layout-column-2\">\n    <div class=\"col-12 col-md-12\">\n        <div class=\"py-5 mb-4\">\n            <div class=\"py-4 pl-2\">\n                <h3 class=\"h3 bottom-title\">4 days later</h3>\n                <h1 class=\"text-main line-after\">Love Handles</h1>\n                <p class=\"text-blue-main text-italic\">These photographs demonstrate the change that is possible with the Sciton ProLipo PLUS™ for laser liposuction.</p>\n<p>The blue oval shapes block identifying marks on the front of this patient. These first two photos were taken only 4 days apart. Over time additional improvement could be expected as the swelling goes down. photo of post operative love handles from the front\nOnly 4 days later\n\nThere is really very little bruising which is not always possible.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>",
