          "726ac02a-798b-4d3e-b7de-c1fc5eedf004": {
            "type": "html",
            "settings": {
              "code": "<div class=\"row align-items-center layout-column-2\">\n    <div class=\"col-12 col-md-12\">\n        <div class=\"py-5\">\n            <div class=\"py-4 pl-2\">\n                <h3 class=\"h3 bottom-title\">male Patient</h3>\n                <h3 class=\"text-main line-after\">Single Laser<br>Peel Treatment</h3>\n                <p class=\"text-blue-main text-italic\">Gentleman with striking improvement from a laser peel.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>",
              "width": "33%",
              "align": "auto"
            }
          },
          "4fc968b9-5bec-4b0a-b170-b3cdd823ffeb": {
            "type": "html",
            "settings": {
              "code": "<div class=\"container\">\n    <div class=\"row m-b-n30\">\n        <div class=\"col-12\">\n            <div class=\"service-long-title text-center\">\n              <h2 class=\"title\">\n                <span class=\"text-main\">Frequently</span> Asked Questions on <span class=\"text-main\">Laser Peel.</span>\n              </h2>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"col-12 col-lg-6 col-el-4 m-b-30\">\n            <div class=\"single-service\">\n                <div class=\"single-service-title\">\n                  <h2 class=\"title\">Does a Laser Peel hurt?</h2>\n                  <p>It can but this is controlled by applying a topical facial cream that numbs the skin. Most people can tolerate the pain with little difficulty resulting in an effective and safe treatment.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"col-12 col-lg-6 col-el-4 m-b-30\">\n            <div class=\"single-service\">\n                <div class=\"single-service-title\">\n                  <h2 class=\"title\">Is it expensive?</h2>\n                  <p>Not really especially when compared to the alternatives such as a surgical face lift. The cost depends on what we peel and also how deep a peel your skin will require. The range is between $625 - $2250 and this will vary on the depth of the peel, the amount of tightening needed, including the eyelids etc.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"col-12 col-lg-6 col-el-4 m-b-30\">\n            <div class=\"single-service\">\n                <div class=\"single-service-title\">\n                  <h2 class=\"title\">What areas can be treated?</h2>\n                  <p>Laser peels can be done on any skin areas. This treatment is mostly done for the face but the hands and upper chest produces nice results as well. Stretch marks, burn scars and surgical scars are treated with laser peels and laser resurfacing.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"col-12 col-lg-6 col-el-4 m-b-30\">\n            <div class=\"single-service\">\n                <div class=\"single-service-title\">\n                  <h2 class=\"title\">What about a laser peel for men?</h2>\n                  <p>Men do have laser peels. Generally men have much more reason to have a laser peel than women.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"col-12 col-lg-6 col-el-4 m-b-30\">\n            <div class=\"single-service\">\n                <div class=\"single-service-title\">\n                  <h2 class=\"title\">Is a picture required?</h2>\n                  <p>No but we'd prefer you did. We will treat you with or without before and after photographs. We will not use the photographs for any reason without your permission.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"col-12 col-lg-6 col-el-4 m-b-30\">\n            <div class=\"single-service\">\n                <div class=\"single-service-title\">\n                  <h2 class=\"title\">Is anesthesia used?</h2>\n                  <p>Yes, we can use  numbing cream to numb your tissue. Deeper peels will require local anesthesia.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>",
              "width": "100%",
              "align": "auto"
            }
          }
        },
