          "1b55e71b-e6ff-4eec-9022-0a63478651d7": {
            "type": "html",
            "settings": {
              "code": "<div class=\"row align-items-center layout-column-2\">\n    <div class=\"col-12 col-md-12\">\n        <div class=\"py-5 mb-4\">\n            <div class=\"py-4 pl-2\">\n                <h3 class=\"h3 bottom-title\">Move Forward</h3>\n                <h1 class=\"text-main line-after\">Tummy Tuck<br> Procedure</h1>\n                <p class=\"text-blue-main text-italic\">Don't let frustrating fat areas impact how you feel about your body.</p>\n<p>While diet and exercise are certainly good ways to enjoy a healthy body, occasionally we run into areas that simply do not respond to them. If you have excess skin or fat in your abdomen, Rebe offers a tummy tuck which is also referred to as an abdominoplasty procedure.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>",
              "width": "50%",
              "align": "auto"
            }
          },
          "fd9c1071-582d-4a31-8094-9ae0408abcf5": {
            "type": "html",
            "settings": {
              "code": "<div class=\"row align-items-center layout-column-2\">\n    <div class=\"col-12 col-md-12\">\n        <div class=\"py-5 mb-4\">\n            <div class=\"py-4 pl-2\">\n                <h3 class=\"h3 bottom-title\">Simple & Fast</h3>\n                <h1 class=\"text-main line-after\">Is a Tummy Tuck<br> Right For Me?</h1>\n                <p class=\"text-blue-main text-italic\">We at Rebe are trained in finding the best options for each patient.</p>\n<p>We will schedule at least two preoperative consultations with you, during which time we’ll discuss your options in detail and determine whether or not a tummy tuck is right for you. Tummy tucks are not weight loss procedures; instead, they're designed to get rid of stubborn pockets of fat that don't respond to diet or exercise. They're best suited to patients who are at or near their ideal weight. It can be used as a solution to the stubborn pockets of extra skin and fat that persist despite your healthy lifestyle choices.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>",
              "width": "50%",
              "align": "auto"
            }
          },
          "61d19758-5506-467b-acd9-25a0b898ac89": {
            "type": "html",
            "settings": {
              "code": "<div class=\"elfsight-sapp-89caa6b8-692a-45bc-a82e-da0806b93c2f\"></div>",
              "width": "50%",
              "align": "auto"
            }
          },
          "4f3825db-6052-4a97-a52b-b435419a483a": {
            "type": "html",
            "settings": {
              "code": "<div class=\"text-center row align-items-center layout-column-2\">\n    <div class=\"col-12 col-md-12\">\n        <div class=\"py-5 mb-4\">\n            <div class=\"py-4 pl-2\">\n                <h1 class=\"text-main line-after\">Preparation for a Tummy Tuck</h1>\n                <p class=\"text-blue-main text-italic\">Our staff will gladly answer any questions you have before and after the procedure.</p>\n<p>A tummy tuck procedure, which is also known as an abdominoplasty, varies greatly from patient to patient. Not only do each patient present with highly unique physical and anatomical characteristics, but they also each have unique cosmetic goals. Our goal at Re*be® is to give you a peace of mind while helping you tackle problem areas.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>",
              "width": "100%",
              "align": "auto"
            }
          }
        },
