      "advanced-content-page-4": {
        "type": "advanced-content-page-4",
        "blocks": {
          "0b1f22f5-c0de-468e-8f8c-8b4b6ef72d6b": {
            "type": "html",
            "settings": {
              "code": "<div class=\"row align-items-center layout-column-2\">\n    <div class=\"col-12 col-md-12\">\n        <div class=\"py-5 mb-4\">\n            <div class=\"py-4 pl-2\">\n                <h3 class=\"h3 bottom-title\">Change Everything</h3>\n                <h1 class=\"text-main line-after\">Breast Reduction</h1>\n                <p class=\"text-blue-main text-italic\">Breast Reduction can be submitted to insurance if medically necessary.</p>\n<p>Breasts that are too large can present a number of problems, and they are not always cosmetic. Being unable to fit into the clothes you want to wear is frustrating, but it can be even more frustrating to suffer back pain because of the strain your breasts place on your upper body muscles. At Re*be, our team of surgeons is able to perform the breast reduction surgery with results that are right for you. This procedure will allow you to reduce your bust size so that it's proportionate to your body, enabling you to enjoy life to the fullest.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>",
              "width": "50%",
              "align": "auto"
            }
          },
          "05a3f7e2-9dc6-4160-a0a4-b97b69827cc0": {
            "type": "image",
            "settings": {
              "width": "50%",
              "align": "auto",
              "image": "shopify://shop_images/Surgical_Procedures_Lady.webp",
              "image_link": ""
            }
          },
          "cc10e914-48b6-4eef-a2c6-edeb45ca4519": {
            "type": "html",
            "settings": {
              "code": "<div class=\"container service_special-exo\">\n    <div class=\"row m-b-n30\">\n        <div class=\"col-12\">\n            <div class=\"service-long-title text-center\">\n              <h2 class=\"title\">\n                <span class=\"text-main\">Breast Reduction</span> Frequently Asked Questions\n              </h2>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"col-12 col-lg-6 col-el-4 m-b-30\">\n            <div class=\"single-service\">\n                <div class=\"single-service-title\">\n                  <h2 class=\"title\">How long is the procedure?</h2>\n                  <p>The length of the procedure varies from person to person. Despite being under general anesthesia, you'll be able to go home the same day, where you'll relax and recuperate in the comfort of your own home.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"col-12 col-lg-6 col-el-4 m-b-30\">\n            <div class=\"single-service\">\n                <div class=\"single-service-title\">\n                  <h2 class=\"title\">When will I see a difference?</h2>\n                  <p>Recovery from a breast reduction is fairly straightforward, and you’ll notice a decrease in your bust size immediately.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"col-12 col-lg-6 col-el-4 m-b-30\">\n            <div class=\"single-service\">\n                <div class=\"single-service-title\">\n                  <h2 class=\"title\">Post-Surgery: What should I expect?</h2>\n                  <p>Recovery time varies from patient to patient. Some mild tenderness and bruising is be completely normal. You will need to purchase a post-surgical support bra to keep your breasts in place as you heal.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"col-12 col-lg-6 col-el-4 m-b-30\">\n            <div class=\"single-service\">\n                <div class=\"single-service-title\">\n                  <h2 class=\"title\">Does a breast reduction include a lift?</h2>\n                  <p>A breast reduction invloves the removal of excess fat and tissue while a breast lift involves the reshaping the breast. We will discuss the best option for you and if a lift is needed with your breast reduction.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>",
              "width": "100%",
              "align": "auto"
            }
          },
          "7bfaac83-fda4-4330-827e-e3700f9c9a8b": {
            "type": "html",
            "settings": {
              "code": "<div class=\"row align-items-center layout-column-2\">\n    <div class=\"col-12 col-md-12\">\n        <div class=\"py-5\">\n            <div class=\"py-4 pl-2\">\n                <h3 class=\"h3 bottom-title\">Breast Reduction Surgery</h3>\n                <h3 class=\"text-main line-after\">Breast Reduction<br>\nProcedure Video</h3>\n                <p class=\"text-blue-main text-italic\">Watch our detailed video on a breast reduction procedure.</p>\n<p>Contact us today to learn more information about our different breast reduction procedures we offer at Rebe.</p>\n<button type=\"submit\" class=\"btn btn-theme\" name=\"commit\"><a href=\"https://www.coolsculpting.com\">\n                        <span class=\"d-none d-sm-block text-white\">Contact Us</span>\n                        <span class=\"d-block d-sm-none\"><i class=\"icon-send\"></i></span>\n                      </a></button>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>",
              "width": "33%",
              "align": "auto"
            }
          },
