            "type": "html",
            "settings": {
              "code": "<div class=\"row align-items-center layout-column-2\">\n    <div class=\"col-12 col-md-12\">\n        <div class=\"py-5 mb-4\">\n            <div class=\"py-4 pl-2\">\n                <h3 class=\"h3 bottom-title\">Offering the bEST</h3>\n                <h1 class=\"text-main line-after\">Dermatology<br>Services</h1>\n                <p class=\"\">The staff and health care providers at re*be® are highly trained and certified. We have 2 MDs on staff, a Surgeon, Dr. Ronald Kolegraff MD and a Family practitioner, Dr. Julie Hamann MD.  If you have skin conditions and want or need to see a physician about, schedule an appointment at  re*be<sup>®</sup>  now.</p>\n<p>We will gladly help you choose the best way to address any of your skin , vein or cosmetic health concerns.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>",
