          "2d89de88-98f3-4fe8-a41f-b3d4b61bb781": {
            "type": "html",
            "settings": {
              "code": "<div class=\"row align-items-center layout-column-2\">\n    <div class=\"col-12 col-md-12\">\n        <div class=\"py-5 mb-4\">\n            <div class=\"py-4 pl-2\">\n                <h3 class=\"h3 bottom-title\">How it Works</h3>\n                <h1 class=\"text-main line-after\">Blepharoplasty</h1>\n                <p class=\"text-blue-main text-italic\">Our office is happy to answer any questions or concerns you may have.</p>\n<p>Blepharoplasty is a minimally invasive surgical procedure done in our office under local anesthesia to improve the appearance of the eyelids.  Excess skin on the eyelid is removed to treat loose or sagging skin that disturbs the natural contour of the upper eyelid, sometimes impairing vision. For more information we recommend a consult with Dr. Kolegraff. </p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>",
