      "advanced-content-page-5-9": {
        "type": "advanced-content-page-5-9",
        "blocks": {
          "37ea09de-02da-4f85-afc8-e10f09542d87": {
            "type": "image",
            "settings": {
              "width": "50%",
              "align": "auto",
              "image": "shopify://shop_images/biote-age-happier.webp",
              "image_link": ""
            }
          },
          "b3facf72-e78a-4841-9d8b-acc86d6533e3": {
            "type": "html",
            "settings": {
              "code": "<div class=\"row align-items-center layout-column-2\">\n    <div class=\"col-12 col-md-12\">\n        <div class=\"py-5 mb-4\">\n            <div class=\"py-4 pl-2\">\n                <h3 class=\"h3 bottom-title\">Why Natural is Better</h3>\n                <h1 class=\"text-main line-after\">Biote Hormone<br> Therapy</h1>\n                <p class=\"text-blue-main text-italic\">Our providers wanted to offer a more natural way for patients<br>to receive hormone therapy.</p>\n<p>Biote Hormone therapy is a natural hormone replacement that is done in pellet form. We\nintroduced this treatment option to our clinic November 2021. Bioidentical hormone replacement pellet therapy is a personalized approach to hormone replacement. It is a steady release of hormones in your body. We offer a variety of Biote nutraceuticals that can help optimize your hormone treatment therapy.  You can find those at our clinic or at our online store.  </p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>",
              "width": "50%",
              "align": "auto"
            }
          },
          "d46614cb-c9ca-4090-bc85-6ec199058ced": {
            "type": "html",
            "settings": {
              "code": "<div class=\"row align-items-center layout-column-2\">\n  <div class=\"col-12 col-md-12\">\n    <div class=\"py-5 mb-4\">\n      <div class=\"py-4 pl-2\">\n        <h3 class=\"h3 bottom-title\">Start Your Journey Now!</h3>\n        <h3 class=\"text-main line-after\">How do you know if you<br> are a candidate?</h3>\n        <p class=\"text-blue-main text-italic\">Biote hormone therapy is for both men and women who maybe experiencing signs of:</p>\n        <p>\n          </p>\n<ul class=\"customMold-list\">\n            <li>\n              <span class=\"titleMole\">- Low Energy</span>\n            </li>\n            <li>\n              <span class=\"titleMole\">- Depression or Anxiety</span>\n            </li>\n            <li>\n              <span class=\"titleMole\">- Lowered Sex Drive</span>\n            </li>\n            <li>\n              <span class=\"titleMole\">- Weight Gain</span>\n            </li>\n          </ul>\n          <ul class=\"customMold-list\">\n            <li>\n              <span class=\"titleMole\">- Hot Flashes</span>\n            </li>\n            <li>\n              <span class=\"titleMole\">- Night Sweats</span>\n            </li>\n            <li>\n              <span class=\"titleMole\">- Not Sleeping Well</span>\n            </li>\n            <li>\n              <span class=\"titleMole\">- Joint pain</span>\n            </li>\n          </ul>\n\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>",
              "width": "50%",
              "align": "auto"
            }
          },
          "bfc9096b-4a4b-4f6b-a3b1-af7df1a17f47": {
            "type": "image",
            "settings": {
              "width": "50%",
              "align": "auto",
              "image": "shopify://shop_images/hormone-balance.webp",
              "image_link": ""
            }
          },
          "d447d8fb-f82f-41d7-83db-4e6771752de2": {
            "type": "html",
            "settings": {
              "code": "<div class=\"row align-items-center layout-column-2\">\n    <div class=\"col-12 col-md-12\">\n        <div>\n            <div class=\"pl-2\">\n                <h3 class=\"h3 bottom-title\">Why Natural is Better</h3>\n                <h1 class=\"text-main line-after\">Biote Hormone<br> Therapy</h1>\n                <p class=\"text-blue-main text-italic\">Pellets are small capsules (about the size of a grain of rice) that contain bioidentical hormones like testosterone or estrogen.</p>\n<p>A bioidentical hormone is the exact molecular structure of hormones the body produces naturally. They are inserted under the skin, where hormones enter the bloodstream as they dissolve over several months. The hormones are released with cardiac output so the more active you are the more your hormones will be released. Bioidentical hormone replacement therapy (BHRT) can come in oral, injections, topical and pellet forms. BHRT using pellets has many advantages over other hormone modalities because this type of therapy does not have the rollercoaster effects of other forms hormone treatment.</p>\n<p>When you use other forms of hormone therapy you have to\nremember to apply or administer but with pellet therapy it is readily available when needed. The pellets dissolve in the body naturally and are made of soy and yams. Women receive 3-4 per year while men will receive 2-3 per year.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>",
              "width": "100%",
              "align": "auto"
            }
          }
        },
